Business Brief -- Johnson Controls Inc.:
   Plant in Wales That Makes
   Plastic Containers Is Bought
The plant, which supplies plastic preforms to soft drink
bottlers in the U.K., gives Johnson Controls a "presence" in
that country, the company said. The U.K. is the largest
plastic container market in Europe; Johnson Controls already
operates plastics facilities in Belgium and Italy.
   Johnson Controls, Milwaukee, is a supplier of plastic
bottles to the U.S. market, in addition to its interests in
building controls, auto seating and batteries.